reviewText: I have MS and this DVD really made me feel a lot better I was Katrina had different ones I rotate each day with a different level thank you for helping

This is an exceptional DVD for low, mid, and high mobility patients with chronic illness. However, this DVD is free from MS active source, the organization who created it and ships to patients free. Visit this link to order DVD for free; [...]

I have Multiple Sclerosis and this is a great way to exercise no matter what level of your disability is and how old you are. There are three levels (it goes from easy to hard)and each one has a resting period. You don't have to have a cooling jacket unless you are exercising in a hot area. I highly recommend this DVD, although the price here is ridiculous! You can get it for free at the msactivesource.com website.
